    "description": "HCL Technologies has an exciting opening for a Senior Software Engineer at our Bhopal office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout HCL Technologies:\nHCL Technologies is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Docker\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Learning & development budget\n• Flexible working hours\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HCL Technologies!",
